{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"545dd534ed","title":"鸣放诗——请出来吧！你！","origin":"《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c296989cb","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"545dd534ed"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"},{"id":"fca557d56d","name":"牛蒡草(刘金堂)"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"61c76c7b5e","type":"title","text":"鸣放诗——请出来吧！你！","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"8e6dbc1667","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院牛蒡草(刘金堂)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"19268347d2","type":"subtitle","text":"（刘金堂：中央民族学院语文系一年级藏语班学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"f6e13f7942","type":"subtitle","text":"请出来吧！你！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"3a712898b1","type":"subtitle","text":"牛蒡草(刘金堂)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"89e786f19b","type":"paragraph","text":"请出来吧！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"ffaa8a012a","type":"paragraph","text":"离开你的深宫下院，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"09087ff2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"“万岁们”，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"39a8226605","type":"paragraph","text":"今日的“中国女皇”!","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"d890efe5c0","type":"paragraph","text":"已经过时了","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"d53986242f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的威力——","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"2546e14ab7","type":"paragraph","text":"几句闲话：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"7f3769b0de","type":"paragraph","text":"令百花在冬天齐放；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"1904118a37","type":"paragraph","text":"因为不满意：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"d6a741575a","type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹充军洛阳。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"d8cafe0c96","type":"paragraph","text":"抛弃那清高的宝座，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"3691750602","type":"paragraph","text":"脱去那华丽的衣冠，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"734f9f1580","type":"paragraph","text":"让你们的龙足","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"89c49f7bd5","type":"paragraph","text":"踏一踏这春天的绿草，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"162f26d13b","type":"paragraph","text":"让这二十世纪的阳光；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"4f939e6be9","type":"paragraph","text":"照一照你苍白的脸。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"7ca85f8a56","type":"paragraph","text":"去吧!拿起锄头","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"996cded142","type":"paragraph","text":"作一个勤朴的园丁——","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"15c47fcb7c","type":"paragraph","text":"用你的双手","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"3bb0475af8","type":"paragraph","text":"去扶一扶那歪斜的花枝；","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"8f2ef7d613","type":"paragraph","text":"用你的双手","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"737bb73836","type":"paragraph","text":"引进那清净的水泉。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"0fb1ef8c35","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么你缩手缩脚？","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"96b43becec","type":"paragraph","text":"难道你害怕春天?","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"0f74cd9eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"看，青春的烈火已经燃烧了，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"8a0780646c","type":"paragraph","text":"它会将你的一切焚毁。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"bfdb2b9441","type":"paragraph","text":"在你的皇宫的废嘘上，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"ee1e5050df","type":"paragraph","text":"开出了千紫万红的花朵，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"7c09e932d5","type":"paragraph","text":"而代替你那怯弱颤抖的","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"746c285a13","type":"paragraph","text":"将是那震撼宇宙的歌声！","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"},{"id":"fbd55006fa","type":"paragraph","text":" (录自“野草”第1期)","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed"}],"page":{"id":"75729ae30a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"545dd534ed","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}